# Enterprise Context Navigation Standard (Architecture Freeze)

## Three-column model

1. **Column 1 — Primary Navigation** (frozen order — do not change without approval):
   Dashboard · CHANAKYA Radar · Contacts · My Deals · Loan Workspace · Investments · Tasks · Documents · Lenders · Accounting · Mission Control · Horizon · Administration · Settings.
   Fixed height — **never** expand child menus inline.
2. **Column 2 — Context Navigation Panel**: children of Administration / Settings only.
3. **Column 3 — Workspace**: selected screen.

## Module responsibilities (one each)

| Module | Responsibility |
|--------|----------------|
| Dashboard | KPIs |
| CHANAKYA Radar | AI prioritisation / deal health (Kanban only; no drag) |
| My Deals | User work queue (Kanban / List / Table) |
| Loan Workspace | Execution (benches retained) |
| Lender Pipeline | Workflow (inside deal) |

## Contacts (Enterprise Party Registry)

- One Contacts module (`/contacts`). No separate Directory.
- Source of truth: ECM Contact Registry.

## Loan Board

- **Removed.** `/pipeline` redirects to CHANAKYA Radar.
- Do not reintroduce Loan Board in primary nav.

## Administration

- Configuration only.
- **Never** park operational workspaces under Administration.

## Behaviour

- Context domain parents open Column 2.
- Source of truth: `src/config/navigation.ts`.
